Prexus Server</font></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000044><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/utienencrazywolf.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Tienen Crazywolf</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(9/20/00 11:55:25 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/fbenevolentordergeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=129.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   New thoughts</span><hr size=1> Well, seeing how this was taken it seems I shall lower the level requirements. The main thing i was trying to do was try and keep our numbers down a little bit, as recently we had a rather nice sized influx of lower level players. Now, there is nothing wrong with that, but i was trying to attract a larger crowd so to speak. From what I gather, korlak and myself are the only 2 high level players Left in Benevolent order.Ill think about a change in requirements that would be more fit to this feedback i have recieved.<br>
Tienen Crazywolf <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/fbenevolentordergeneral.showPrevMessage?topicID=129.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/fbenevolentordergeneral.showNextMessage?topicID=129.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/fbenevolentordergeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=129.topic&index=6><img src=http://bo.c-g8.com:8088/graphics/replybutton.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/fbenevolentordergeneral.emailToFriend?topicID=129.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/fbenevolentordergeneral.threadControl?topicID=129.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/egyptian/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/fbenevolentordergeneral.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=129.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/fbenevolentordergeneral.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=129.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub11.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="benevolentordergeneral">General<option value="benevolentordereventplanning">Event Planning<option value="benevolentorderfrm9">Epic Quests<option value="benevolentorderfrm6">Trade Skills<option value="benevolentorderdungeonchat">Dungeon Chat<option